<h1>UniMag University Magazine<h1>

This is the University Magazine system.
The system allows users with secure roles.

Navigate to <b>`login.php`</b> to access the system.

<h2>System Configuration Instructions<h2>

The system uses a .env file for email configuration. As per security concerns, the gmail account name and app password has to be configured while testing.

To enable email notifications:

1. Use a Gmail account

Replace:
<b>MAIL_USERNAME=yourname@gmail.com</b>
<b>MAIL_FROM=yourname@gmail.com<b>
with gmail account name

2. Generate App Password
   Go to Google Account → Security
   Enable 2-Step Verification
   Create App Password

3. Then update:

<b>MAIL_PASSWORD=your_generated_app_password</b>
